Step 2: Implement 💻 Execute the 3 Tasks:
After I give my confirmation, implement only the three approved tasks. Focused
Implementation: Keep the code changes strictly focused on the approved items to
ensure the pull request is small and easy to review.
Step 3: Review & Repeat 🔄
Update Plan: After completing the implementation, update the
implementation_plan.md file by marking the corresponding tasks as completed
(e.g., - [x] Task Description). Submit Work: Submit all your changes for my
review, including the updated implementation_plan.md file. Propose Next 3
Tasks: In the same message, show me the next 3 unchecked items from the
implementation_plan.md. Await Next Go-Ahead: I will review your completed code
and the updated plan while also approving the next set of tasks. Wait for my
confirmation before starting the next implementation cycle. This process
repeats until all items in implementation_plan.md are marked as complete.
